A collaboration between Medwyn Goodall, Terry Oldfield and friends.

Recorded in 11 recording studio&#039;s across the world including Australia, England, Sweden, Poland, and the Czech Republic, never before has there been such a gathering of artists composing and performing original material together on an album.
OM goes way beyond what was expected or anticipated, what has emerged is a performance of sheer beauty and incredible expression.
